<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>
    <%= title %>
  </title>

  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">

  <!-- CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/header.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css">

</head>

<body>

  <!-- ===== HEADER ===== -->
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <!-- ===== HERO SECTION ===== -->
    <main class="home-page">
      <section class="hero">

        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <div class="hero-content">
          <span class="hero-badge">Natural Looking Hair Restoration</span>
          <h1>EVA CLINIC</h1>
          <h2>Best in Hair Density & Skin Therapy in Lucknow</h2>
          
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ===== RATINGS SECTION ===== -->
      <section class="ratings">
        <div class="rating-box">
          <img src="/img/google.jpg" alt="Google Rating">
          <div>
            <span class="score">4.8</span>
            <p>Google</p>
            <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rating-box">
          <img src="img/proven-expert.webp" alt="Proven Expert Rating">
          <div>
            <span class="score">4.8</span>
            <p>Proven Expert</p>
            <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rating-box">
          <img src="  /img/realself.jpg" alt="RealSelf Rating">
          <div>
            <span class="score">5.0</span>
            <p>RealSelf</p>
            <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rating-box">
          <img src="/img/trustpilot.webp" alt="Trustpilot Rating">
          <div>
            <span class="score">4.8</span>
            <p>Trustpilot</p>
            <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <!-- ===== OUR SPECIAL FEATURE SECTION ===== -->
      <section class="special-feature">
        <div class="container-feature">
          <h2>Our Special Feature</h2>

          <div class="feature-grid">

            <div class="feature-box">
              <img src="/img/75.png" alt="Consultant Icon">
              <h3>65</h3>
              <p>Expert Consultants</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box">
              <img src="/img/2000.png" alt="Reviews Icon">
              <h3>2,000</h3>
              <p>Excellent Reviews</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box">
              <img src="/img/3000.jpg" alt="Patients Icon">
              <h3>10,000+</h3>
              <p>Patients Worldwide</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box">
              <img src="/img/Experience.jpg" alt="Experience Icon">
              <h3>12</h3>
              <p>Years of Experience</p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <!-- ===== BEST HAIR TRANSPLANT SECTION ===== -->
      <section class="hair-transplant-info">
        <div class="container-hair">
          <h2>
            Best Hair Transplant in LUCKNOW at EVA CLINIC:
            <span>World-Class Service</span>
          </h2>

          <p class="intro-text">
            At our clinic, we specialize in world-class hair transplants that combine advanced technology with expert
            care. Our minimally invasive procedures deliver natural-looking results by restoring hair from dense growth
            areas to thinning regions — effectively reversing hair loss and bringing back your confidence
          </p>

          <div class="results-gallery">
            <div class="result-card">
              <img src="/img/result1.png" alt="Before and After Hair Transplant">
            </div>
            <div class="result-card">
              <img src="/img/result2.png" alt="Before and After Hair Transplant">
            </div>
            <div class="result-card">
              <img src="/img/result3.png" alt="Before and After Hair Transplant">
            </div>
            <div class="result-card">
              <img src="/img/result4.png" alt="Before and After Hair Transplant">
            </div>

          </div>

          <p class="bottom-text">
            Hair transplants are rapidly gaining popularity as more people discover the benefits of choosing Lucknow for
            world-class treatment. Our advanced, minimally invasive hair transplant procedures effectively restore
            natural hair by relocating follicles from dense areas to regions of hair loss — reversing baldness,
            revitalizing confidence, and delivering lasting, natural results.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <!-- ===== VIDEO SECTION ===== -->
      <section class="video-section">
        <div class="container-videos">
          <div class="videos">
            <!-- Video 1 -->
            <div class="video-box">
              <img src="/img/youtube2..png" alt="Hair Transplant Clinic Video">
              <a href="https://youtube.com/shorts/A1jUBiySGQ0?si=XMbb9Ehznag8g3QG" target="_blank" class="play-btn">
                <img src="/img/play-icon.png" alt="Play Icon">
              </a>
              <div class="video-title">
                <h3>HAIR TRANSPLANT EVA CLINIC IN LUCKNOW</h3>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Video 2 -->
            <div class="video-box">
              <img src="/img/youtube2..png" alt="Hair Transplant Video">
              <a href="https://youtube.com/shorts/dQR5O6MyZ-Q?si=9WooFjIrFoATvJ4Z" target="_blank" class="play-btn">
                <img src="/img/play-icon.png" alt="Play Icon">
              </a>
              <div class="video-title">
                <h3>HAIR TRANSPLANT EVA CLINIC IN LUCKNOW</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ===== CLINIC IMAGES SECTION ===== -->
      <section class="clinic-images">
        <div class="container-clinic-images">
          <h2>Clinic Images</h2>
          <div class="gallery">
            <img src="/img/5.1.png" alt="Clinic Image 1">
            <img src="/img/5.2.png" alt="Clinic Image 2">
            <img src="/img/5.3.png" alt="Clinic Image 3">
            <img src="/img/5.4.png" alt="Clinic Image 4">
            <img src="/img/5.5.png" alt="Clinic Image 5">
            <img src="/img/5.6.png" alt="Clinic Image 6">
            
            
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>-
      <section class="team-section">
        <h1 class="section-title">Our Team</h1>
        <p class="section-desc">
          <strong>EVA CLINIC</strong> stands among the world’s leading hair transplant centers, known for excellence,
          innovation, and trust. With a team of highly skilled and experienced specialists, our clinic combines medical
          expertise with advanced technology to deliver outstanding, natural-looking results. At Vaanya Clinic, we use
          the latest techniques and state-of-the-art equipment to ensure every patient receives personalized care and
          long-lasting outcomes. Renowned for precision, artistry, and exceptional success rates, our doctors are
          dedicated to restoring not just hair — but confidence. If you’re seeking the best in hair restoration,
          <strong>EVA CLINIC</strong> is your destination for excellence.
        </p>

        <div class="team-gallery">
          <div class="team-img">
            <img src="img/team1.jpeg" alt="Team 1">
          </div>
          <div class="team-img">
            <img src="img/team3.png" alt="Team 2">
          </div>
          <div class="team-img">
            <img src="/img/team2.png" alt="Team 3">
          </div>
          
      </div>
        </div>
      </section>



    </main>

    <!-- ===== FOOTER ===== -->
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

</body>

</html>
